title: august 20: welcome to bayside high (with AmandaRachLee)
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the hit teen TV show Saved by the Bell, which premiered on NBC on this date in 1989 and ran for four seasons. After, she talks to guest AmandaRachLee. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
